('Bulleit Bourbon', 'Kentucky, United States', 45, 'Dried fruit, oak, and a peppery warmth from the rye.','Dried fruit, oak, and a peppery warmth from the rye.', 'Bulleit Bourbon is inspired by the whiskey that was pioneered by Augustus Bulleit over 150 years ago. Only ingredients of the very highest quality are used. The complexity of Bulleit Bourbon comes from its unique blend of rye, corn, and barley malt, along with special strains of yeast.'),
('Jack Daniels Old No.7', 'Tennessee, United States', 40, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Jack Daniels Tennessee Whiskey is the worlds best selling whiskey, with every bottle distilled and bottled at the Jack Daniel Distillery in Lynchburg, Tennessee, Americas oldest registered distillery, established in 1866.'),
('Makers Mark', 'Tennessee, United States', 45, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Makers Mark started with bread, of course. Bill Samuels bought the Burks Distillery in Loretto, Kentucky, in 1953 and did the predictable ...just not in a predictable way.' ),
('Jim Beam (Bourbon Whiskey)', 'United States', 40, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Founded in 1795 and passed down through one family for the past seven generations, Jim Beam is the worlds best-selling bourbon. From Tokyo to London to Louisville, Jim Beam sets the benchmark for what a bourbon should be.'),
('Basil Haydens (Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey)', 'Kentucky, United States', 40, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Marked by a rich cascade of aromas and flavors, Basil Haydens速 Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey is carefully matured for exceptional quality and distilled in the heart of bourbon country in Clermont, Kentucky.'),
('Woodford Reserve (Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey)', 'Kentucky, United States', 45, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Woodford Reserve is built around flavor. The art of making fine bourbon first took place on the site of the Woodford Reserve Distillery, a National Historic Landmark, in 1812. The perfectly balanced taste of our Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey is composed of more than 200 detectable notes.'),
('Knob Creek (Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whiskey)', 'Kentucky, United States', 50, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Knob Creek Bourbon has some good blood. Not only is it named after the boyhood home of Abraham Lincoln, it has some highly acclaimed brothers in the Jim Beam family: Bookers, Basil Haydens and Bakers. Aged nine years, Knob Creek is the oldest by a couple years.'),
('Buffalo Trace', 'Kentucky, United States', 45, 'Anise, Dark Fruit, Mint, Sweet, Vanilla, Brown sugar', 'N/A', 'Ancient buffalo carved paths through the wilderness that led American pioneers and explorers to new frontiers. One such trail led to the banks of the Kentucky River where Buffalo Trace Distillery has been making bourbon whiskey the same way for more than 200 years.'),
('Evan Williams', 'Kentucky, United States', 43, 'Caramel, Oak', 'Beef, Cheese-Hard Aged, Nuts', 'You may think you have run the gamut of American bourbons, but if you havent tried Evan Williams Black, you arent quite finished with your foray into one of Americas finest exports. Founded in 1783 on the banks of the Ohio River, Evan Williams is one of the oldest distilleries in the United States.'),  
('Wild Turkey 101', 'Kentucky, United States', 50, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Wild Turkey 101 is different for good reason, and it all comes down to premium ingredients, select barrels, and a lot of patience. Wild Turkey ages the whiskey longer in new American White Oak barrels with the deepest possible char, cutting no corners across all of our bourbons.'),
('Four Roses Bourbon', 'Kentucky, United States', 40, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Four Roses Bourbon blends up to 10 of our distinct Bourbon recipes, resulting in a versatile, easy-drinking Bourbon that appeals to casual fans and enthusiasts alike. Perfect for cocktails. Crafted from up to 10 of our distinct Bourbon recipes 80 proof Aged 5 years minimum.' ),
('Elijah Craig (Small Batch Bourbon)', 'Kentucky, United States', 47, 'Mint, Nutmeg, Smokey, Sweet, Toasty, Vanilla', 'Beef, CHeese-Hard Aged, Dessert-Chocolate', 'Elijah Craig is credited as the first distiller to age his whiskey in charred oak barrels, earning his place in history as the Father of Bourbon. The charred barrel transformed the clear liquid inside into an intense amber whiskey made rich with the flavors of the wood which we now adore.'),
('Blantons Single Barrel Bodurbon', 'Kentucky, United States', 46, 'Caramel, Honey, Vanilla', 'N/A', 'In the winter of 1881, Albert Bacon Blanton was born into one of the first families of bourbon history. At the age of sixteen, he started work in the Distillery as an office boy and fast became a leading pioneer in the development of bourbon.' ),
('Makers 46', 'Kentucky, United States', 47, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Makers 46 was created by Bill Samuels, Jr., to amplify the flavors he loves in Makers Mark. The innovative wood stave finishing process starts with fully matured Makers Mark速 at cask strength. We then insert seared virgin French oak staves into the barrel and finish it a bit longer.'),
('Angels Envy', 'Kentucky, United States', 43, 'Chocolate, Toasty, Vanilla', 'N/A', 'Angels Envy is an exceptional Kentucky straight bourbon finished in port wine barrels. Given the Highest Recommendation by Spirit Journal, celebrated by Whisky Advocate, The Bourbon Review, and awarded Wine Enthusiast highest bourbon rating.'),
('Jim Beam (Black)', 'Kentucky, United States', 43, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'Jim Beam Black速 is a premium bourbon with a more flavorful character made to be sipped and savored. Our premium 86-proof, extra-aged bourbon ages years longer in white oak barrels than original Jim Beam速.'),
('Eagle Rare (10yr Bourbon)', 'Kentucky, United States', 45, 'N/A', 'N/A', 'With several awards from the San Francisco World Spirits Competition, Eagle Rare 10 Year isnt your average bourbon. Produced since 1975 in Frankfort, Kentucky, this bourbon is one of the true jewels in the American bourbon scene.'),
('High West American Prairie', 'Utah, United States', 46, 'M/A', 'N/A', 'High West American Prairie Barrel Aged Bourbon Whiskey is a complex blend of straight bourbons, producing an aromatic whiskey that is rich and earthy on the palate. This American bourbon showcases well-balanced flavors of candy corn, honey nougat and sweet corn bread.'),
('Four Roses (Small Batch Bourbon)', 'Kentucky, United States', 45, 'N/A','N/A', 'Four Roses Small Batch combines four of our distinct Bourbon recipes to achieve exceptional balance. Easy to drink neat, on the rocks or as the foundation of a great craft cocktail. A top-shelf staple. Crafted from four of our distinct Bourbon recipes.'),
